title: Team of the Week: Trinity Presbyterian Wildcats
text:
Story Created: Oct 14, 2015 at 11:11 PM CDT 
MONTGOMERY, AL --- This week's Right Stuff Team of the Week is the Trinity Presbyterian Wildcats. 
Coach Randy Ragsdale and his team at Trinity have a 5-3 record this year, with a 4-1 mark in region play. 
They are coming off a 38-21 win over Montgomery Catholic. 
The Wildcat fans went to our website this week, rocked the vote and made them our newest team of the week. You'll see more of the Wildcats this Friday during Mo and Longshore.
